for_final_project

Class BirthInfoCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • for_final_project.BirthInfoCollection

  • public class BirthInfoCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    A BirthInfoCollection object defines a collection of BirthInfos as an alphabetically ordered binary tree of BirthInfos and a chronologically ordered binary tree of BirthInfos.
    Author:
    Kristin Jones

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      BirthInfoCollection()
      Creates a BirthInfoCollection by constructing one binary tree of alphabetically ordered BirthInfos with the 0-parameter BirthInfo constructor and one binary tree of chronologically ordered BirthInfos with the 1-parameter BirthInfo constructor.
